{"type":"text","timestamp":1778639834451,"sessionID":"ses_1e0ce96a4ffeI725GK5eP7uNWf","part":{"id":"prt_e1f320c8e001i6IRJuItRF5CCq","messageID":"msg_e1f31bdc60015nHHRWrPI8SJyr","sessionID":"ses_1e0ce96a4ffeI725GK5eP7uNWf","type":"text","text":"The strongest micro_opt angle is the ALU’s three parallel multiplier products. A single unsigned 32x32 product can serve `MUL`, `MULHU`, `MULH`, and `MULHSU` with standard high-half sign corrections, preserving single-cycle MUL latency while reducing multiplier/routing pressure.","time":{"start":1778639834254,"end":1778639834449},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0a54bb25a5508144016a03e3da2690819891c8363106aa36e7","phase":"commentary"}}}}
