{"type":"text","timestamp":1778651653334,"sessionID":"ses_1e01b7558ffey1JQ9pYmA0GhMu","part":{"id":"prt_e1fe6615c002Rc8evBnDLyrmgB","messageID":"msg_e1fe4af9c001DkHQxDcZSXgKvV","sessionID":"ses_1e01b7558ffey1JQ9pYmA0GhMu","type":"text","text":"I’ll write the hypothesis around explicit sign-bit signed-compare logic in the EX/ALU path. It targets a hot, always-present comparator cone without adding pipeline state, predictor policy, or memory-control complexity.","time":{"start":1778651652444,"end":1778651653333},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_020e2ddaf8b4da3f016a0412042f5c8198b9aa31fa860104b2","phase":"commentary"}}}}
