{"type":"text","timestamp":1778652329563,"sessionID":"ses_1e00f9204ffeW3o4DkhsfmWwhG","part":{"id":"prt_e1ff0a8cc001ojRvoPr13Rn5d9","messageID":"msg_e1ff091ab001Jz41RjsDqBw9dh","sessionID":"ses_1e00f9204ffeW3o4DkhsfmWwhG","type":"text","text":"The prior `micro_opt` wins were narrow datapath removals/simplifications; broad repacking, predictor-control changes, comparator rewrites, and multiplier side-unit variants have mostly regressed. I’m going to propose a contained EX datapath cleanup that removes a likely useless combinational multiply cone from non-M-extension ALU operations without changing CPI or pipeline control.","time":{"start":1778652326092,"end":1778652329560},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_066a1fd19d043b76016a0414a5fe48819aa1666d068635a2bd","phase":"commentary"}}}}
