{"type":"text","timestamp":1778655797818,"sessionID":"ses_1dfdae821ffe0qfAq3dM5zxNpf","part":{"id":"prt_e2025a074001FWg7GFe9oVQIs9","messageID":"msg_e202548ed001ykY8YJKlafnjVS","sessionID":"ses_1dfdae821ffe0qfAq3dM5zxNpf","type":"text","text":"The prior log confirms the successful `micro_opt` was a very local MEM datapath simplification, while control repacking, comparator rewrites, forwarding changes, shifter sharing, and predictor policy tweaks mostly regressed. I’m going to propose a similarly local MEM-stage cleanup that reduces non-load memory-path switching/timing without changing pipeline control or the proven byte-lane mux shape.","time":{"start":1778655797364,"end":1778655797817},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_08b66e40d4406bae016a04223541e8819aa699c5faada6d738","phase":"commentary"}}}}
