{"type":"text","timestamp":1778645012566,"sessionID":"ses_1e07ff9a7ffejB7zZWK7wlGy0D","part":{"id":"prt_e1f810fb5001p3S2CZNgRdMq5i","messageID":"msg_e1f8033e2001Ll5G9m2ymhX8Pa","sessionID":"ses_1e07ff9a7ffejB7zZWK7wlGy0D","type":"text","text":"The prior micro-opt history rules out source-use gating and multiplier reshaping, while the successful MEM mux change points to small timing-path simplifications. I’m going to write a narrow regfile reset-removal hypothesis: it targets Fmax/reset fanout without changing CPI, RVFI shape, or x0/write-first behavior.","time":{"start":1778645012405,"end":1778645012564},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_039813ae57d60aef016a03f814503c819985923447292d3311","phase":"commentary"}}}}
