ed store is pending, while younger non-memory instructions can continue.\n+  - file: rtl/core.sv\n+    description: Wire store-buffer pending/block status between MEM and hazard control without changing the nret=1 RVFI port set or existing predictor interfaces.\n","additions":17,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260513-002-r10s1.yaml","time":{"start":1778650233939,"end":1778650233944}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_014e4d87f5ead609016a040c70c0b48199b31ef7aac8d694a8"}},"id":"prt_e1fd098cf0018o1ykimdA935H0","sessionID":"ses_1e0305f9cffej9ukbpSH4ImNgU","messageID":"msg_e1fd08619001UP6B8s6ZmWFZ6a"}}
