{"type":"text","timestamp":1778653661491,"sessionID":"ses_1dffbc90cffeEMgC4FgH8OAZ5u","part":{"id":"prt_e20050875002B33231i2cjTaaO","messageID":"msg_e20045b34001uACm4a6ZyfjUjM","sessionID":"ses_1dffbc90cffeEMgC4FgH8OAZ5u","type":"text","text":"The structural history is dominated by regressions from added front-end control, store buffering, broad retiming, and M-unit side controls. I’m choosing a narrower structural retime that targets decode fanout without touching prediction policy, memory ordering, or multiplier/divider latency.","time":{"start":1778653661301,"end":1778653661490},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0ad96c3f20820773016a0419dd350c819aa07fa538faa8a2c7","phase":"commentary"}}}}
