{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1778650179032,"sessionID":"ses_1e0306013ffea8EiV328ilAJxS","part":{"id":"prt_e1fcfe5d5001qVSWY8loKIJxZg","messageID":"msg_e1fcfe18c001v79rlE09C4jb3v","sessionID":"ses_1e0306013ffea8EiV328ilAJxS","snapshot":"3ad5867f1392be83e4f2e22924f7dc5f5fdd73e7","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"text","timestamp":1778650236930,"sessionID":"ses_1e0306013ffea8EiV328ilAJxS","part":{"id":"prt_e1fd0c546001i6qesadLHH0TSy","messageID":"msg_e1fcfe18c001v79rlE09C4jb3v","sessionID":"ses_1e0306013ffea8EiV328ilAJxS","type":"text","text":"The most relevant prior result is the successful one-entry registered lookahead predictor; later losses mostly came from adding IF lookup complexity or filtering useful updates. I’m writing a narrower predictor hypothesis that keeps the trained behavior but reduces the always-on prediction validation path.","time":{"start":1778650236230,"end":1778650236928},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0da917dacb640f52016a040c7bf878819a8d176f80cea3314c","phase":"commentary"}}}}
{"type":"text","timestamp":1778650300644,"sessionID":"ses_1e0306013ffea8EiV328ilAJxS","part":{"id":"prt_e1fd1bfd3001n9hnrrMX1oXhmM","messageID":"msg_e1fcfe18c001v79rlE09C4jb3v","sessionID":"ses_1e0306013ffea8EiV328ilAJxS","type":"text","text":"The predictor history shows the only successful variant is the current one-entry registered lookahead predictor. I’m going to propose a narrow update-policy change that preserves its IF timing shape and avoids adding entries, compares, decode, or target adders.","time":{"start":1778650300371,"end":1778650300642},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_04183010fca079e1016a040cbc37e0819b876c836f30592a5c","phase":"commentary"}}}}
