{"type":"text","timestamp":1778641973184,"sessionID":"ses_1e0adc51effeSv1hzl81ETFJPA","part":{"id":"prt_e1f52af260017JFeclm5QzFTqW","messageID":"msg_e1f526ef7001BwuIXMi532wnHj","sessionID":"ses_1e0adc51effeSv1hzl81ETFJPA","type":"text","text":"Prior predictor attempts failed because prediction work sat directly on the IF next-PC path. The strongest predictor-only angle is to move static prediction to ID: still removes one of the two taken-branch/jump bubbles, but keeps IF sequential fetch simple.","time":{"start":1778641973030,"end":1778641973182},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0b9be778a27ddf4c016a03ec34ee1c819abf585bab3a1d83f5","phase":"commentary"}}}}
